return ['messages'=>['<p>At the heart of the Parfum lies a special-cut citrine, celebrated for its vibrant golden hue and unparalleled clarity. This semi-precious stone, with its sleek, flowing lines, is a modern interpretation of feminine grace and strength. The meticulous craftsmanship extends beyond to the special cutting of the citrine, ensuring each unique facet reflects light in a way that evokes the silhouette of a woman. The golden hue of the 18K Yellow Gold setting complements the citrine, enhancing the radiant essence of this jewellery creation.</p>'=>'<p>「香水瓶」（Parfum）以一颗特裁黄水晶为核心，其鲜明的金黄色泽与无瑕透明度令人赞叹。这颗半宝石以流畅线条勾勒，展现女性的优雅与坚韧。精湛的切割工艺使每一个切面折射光芒，勾勒出柔美轮廓。18K黄金与黄水晶相得益彰，进一步突显其高雅神韵。   </p>','<p>Come and celebrate the return of a classic with us! Experience our bespoke service, which allows you to customize your Parfum piece, making this legacy jewellery creation truly one-of-a-kind.</p>'=>'<p>与我们一起庆祝经典之作的回归！体验我们的定制服务，定制您独一无二的专属Parfum。 </p>','<p>In the world of fine jewellery, every creation tells a story, weaving together threads of inspiration, craftsmanship, and timeless design. The Parfum is no exception. This exquisite jewellery creation draws its inspiration from the serene beauty of a contemporary muse, gracefully draped in a glittering gold dress on a grand theatre stage. The Parfum embodies the quintessence – luxury, sophistication and the infinite femininity of a beautiful modern lady.</p>'=>'<p>在高级珠宝的世界中，每件作品都在诉说一段故事，交织灵感、工艺与隽永设计。EJI「香水瓶」（Parfum）亦不例外。这款精致珠宝从现代谬思的静谧之美汲取灵感，仿佛一位身著闪耀金色礼服的女子，优雅站立于华丽剧院舞台中央。它凝聚奢华、精致与现代女性无尽魅力的精髓。   </p>','<p>Sophistication in craftsmanship is evident in every detail of the Parfum. The design and special cutting of the citrine stand out with precision, preserving the gemstone’s beauty and unique reflective qualities. This attention to detail transforms our talented designer’s initial inspiration into a paragon of elegance, capturing the essence of femininity and redefining what it means to be truly elegant. Every aspect of this jewellery creation reflects our dedication to excellence as a fine jewellery manufacturer.</p>'=>'<p>「香水瓶」（Parfum）每一处细节皆彰显精湛工艺。黄水晶设计与特裁手法精准无瑕，保留宝石的天然美感与独特反射特性。这种对细节的极致追求，将设计师的灵感化为优雅，捕捉女性魅力本质，重新定义真正的典雅。每个环节，皆体现我们作为高级珠宝制造商对卓越的执著。   </p>','<p>This September, at the prestigious JGW, the Parfum made its grand return, ready to captivate and enchant audiences once more. The Parfum has been one of our iconic collections for more than ten years, standing as a testament to our commitment to excellence and timeless design. Embracing its radiant beauty, the Parfum shines brilliantly, ready to illuminate your journey.</p><p>Discover the Parfum and welcome its return to the spotlight, mesmerizing the world with its stunning beauty and sophistication. Embrace the legacy of this forever icon, where it tells a story of elegance, luxury and timeless beauty.</p>'=>'<p>今年九月，Parfum于享誉盛名的JGW展会华丽回归，再度以其魅力征服观众。作为我们逾十年的标志性系列，Parfum见证了品牌对隽永设计的承诺。其耀眼光芒闪烁，准备照亮您的旅程。  </p><p>诚邀您探索Parfum，迎接它重返镁光灯下的重要时刻。 </p>','A Gem of Inspiration'=>'灵感之宝石','A Return to Classic'=>'经典回归','Craftsmanship Beyond Excellence'=>'卓越的工藝','Follow Us '=>'关注我们  ','editor-text-editor-461114d'=>'<p>今年九月，Parfum于享誉盛名的JGW展会华丽回归，再度以其魅力征服观众。作为我们逾十年的标志性系列，Parfum见证了品牌对隽永设计的承诺。其耀眼光芒闪烁，准备照亮您的旅程。  </p><p>诚邀您探索Parfum，迎接它重返镁光灯下的重要时刻。 </p>','editor-text-editor-691aa82'=>'<p>在高级珠宝的世界中，每件作品都在诉说一段故事，交织灵感、工艺与隽永设计。EJI「香水瓶」（Parfum）亦不例外。这款精致珠宝从现代谬思的静谧之美汲取灵感，仿佛一位身著闪耀金色礼服的女子，优雅站立于华丽剧院舞台中央。它凝聚奢华、精致与现代女性无尽魅力的精髓。   </p>','editor-text-editor-843d631'=>'<p>「香水瓶」（Parfum）每一处细节皆彰显精湛工艺。黄水晶设计与特裁手法精准无瑕，保留宝石的天然美感与独特反射特性。这种对细节的极致追求，将设计师的灵感化为优雅，捕捉女性魅力本质，重新定义真正的典雅。每个环节，皆体现我们作为高级珠宝制造商对卓越的执著。   </p>','editor-text-editor-b7e2ae6'=>'<p>与我们一起庆祝经典之作的回归！体验我们的定制服务，定制您独一无二的专属Parfum。 </p>','editor-text-editor-ed67bef'=>'<p>「香水瓶」（Parfum）以一颗特裁黄水晶为核心，其鲜明的金黄色泽与无瑕透明度令人赞叹。这颗半宝石以流畅线条勾勒，展现女性的优雅与坚韧。精湛的切割工艺使每一个切面折射光芒，勾勒出柔美轮廓。18K黄金与黄水晶相得益彰，进一步突显其高雅神韵。   </p>','title-heading-0393b6f'=>'经典回归','title-heading-09233f7'=>'灵感之宝石','title-heading-552ae02'=>'关注我们  ','title-heading-a60c794'=>'卓越的工